				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">ROM is at the end of the memory map because the processor requires the interrupt vectors to be at $FFF8-FFFF and the stack to be at $0100-01FF. It wasn't really Nintendo's decision.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

